headline: VetsinTech Honors Excellence in Veteran Support at Annual Gala
summary: VetsinTech, the leading national non-profit dedicated to supporting veterans through tech-based education, employment, and entrepreneurship initiatives, celebrated its 11th annual Gala fundraiser by honoring organizations and leaders setting new standards for military veteran support in the technology sector. The evening featured special guests Chuck Todd, former host of NBC's Meet the Press and six-time Emmy Award winner, CBS/KPIX News Anchor Sara Donchey, and Franco Finn, MC/Host and Personali
